<a class="flex items-center text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:text-amber-custom transition-colors" href="#">
                            Details ansehen
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-1 text-sm">arrow_outward</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-8 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-amber-custom transition-all shadow-sm group">
<h3 class="serif text-2xl mb-4 text-primary">Pflegezuschuss</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6 leading-relaxed">Besonderheiten bei der sozialen Pflegepflichtversicherung für Angestellte.</p>
<a class="flex items-center text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:text-amber-custom transition-colors" href="#">
                            Mehr erfahren
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-1 text-sm">arrow_outward</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-8 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-amber-custom transition-all shadow-sm group">
