<a class="font-['Inter'] text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-[#00261c] dark:hover:text-emerald-400 underline decoration-2 transition-opacity opacity-80 hover:opacity-100" href="#">Imprint</a>
</nav>
